For applying any traffic pattern, make the changes as described below:


For TRANSPOSE for tile-i,

	type DESTINATION TRANSPOSE in nirgam/config/traffic/tile-i

For BIT_REVERSAL

	type DESTINATION BIT_REVERSAL in nirgam/config/traffic/tile-i

For BIT_SHUFFLE for tile-i,

	type DESTINATION BIT_SHUFFLE in nirgam/config/traffic/tile-i

For BUTTERFLY for tile-i,

	type DESTINATION BUTTERFLY in nirgam/config/traffic/tile-i

For HOTSPOT for tile-i,
	
	type DESTNATION RANDOM
	type HOTSPOT <Destination tile ID> <Probability> in nirgam/config/traffic/tile-i 

example:

tile-1
DESTINATION TRANSPOSE

then destination will be choosen as: 5

tile-8
DESTINATION BIT_REVERSAL

then destination will be choosen as: 2

tile-12
DESTINATION BIT_SHUFFLE

then destination will be choosen as:24

tile-7
DESTINATION BUTTERFLY

the destination will be choosen as: 22 
